dcterms:description: A dataset containing interactions on job postings for 770,000 users over an 80-day period. User behaviors include click, bookmark, reply, and delete. The dataset is split into sessions by a 30-minute idle threshold.
dcterms:title: Xing Dataset

dcterms:creator: M. Ruocco

H. Langseth
dcterms:description: A dataset containing tuples of user names, subreddits where the user makes a comment to a thread, and a timestamp for the interaction. The dataset is split into sessions by a 60-minute idle threshold.
dcterms:title: Reddit Dataset
